&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;데이터를 크게 두개의 기분으로 분류한다.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Covid case &amp;amp; Demographic Columns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;case_vars &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;location&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;total_cases&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;total_deaths&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;total_cases_pm&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;total_deaths_pm&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;demo_vars &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;population&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;pop_density&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;median_age&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;gdp_per_capita&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hosp_beds&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;axis 설정을 통해 인구통계와 Covid Cased의 결측치 값을 설정한다.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;covidtotals[demo_vars]&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;isnull()&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;sum(axis&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;population 0
pop_density 12
